### ‚ú® New Features
- [`06379d3`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/06379d307dc14de785145bffeb53a2e7caf463ed) - **wallpapers**: ability to set custom name when importing *(commit by @aliernfrog)*
- [`64e5e25`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/64e5e2566c72d69e62c8775c5c97e41050b7b210) - **wallpapers**: show current wallpaper at top *(commit by @aliernfrog)*
- [`1ec4b2d`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/1ec4b2d2263f15bf8beeb96f32eb3058aeea461b) - **wallpapers**: full screen viewer & zooming *(commit by @aliernfrog)*
- [`7bd2188`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/7bd218806d7512fc8f7e360c2f97ac2853bf896e) - **screenshots**: full screen viewer & zooming *(commit by @aliernfrog)*
- [`f939754`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/f939754846e56f2ac5e59f0199b9e885c78d71f0) - **maps**: ability to manage thumbnails *(commit by @aliernfrog)*
- [`da18f4a`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/da18f4a67dd3aa69452837cd506304d1b14f1c85) - **shizuku**: suggest restarting when waiting for too long *(commit by @aliernfrog)*
- [`2516523`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/25165239245f7f7f272ab1d88ce51327da6a9da5) - **maps/materials**: full screen viewer & zooming *(commit by @aliernfrog)*
- [`011a839`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/011a83983d205502e656325cbe8feb4d9b1160b5) - redesign image buttons *(commit by @aliernfrog)*
- [`fbeb029`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/fbeb0291f2224381e229944c94fc2c7cb0cc547b) - grid view & sorting options for lists *(commit by @aliernfrog)*
- [`c067515`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/c0675157f9ec122a3bfa744eeb4cf4189a7f85d8) - add support for Sui *(commit by @aliernfrog)*
- [`ca506f4`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/ca506f4f2e1e7a55d3ada229826a7d27bf62a5ba) - various changes, fixes and refactors *(commit by @aliernfrog)*
- [`6ed71ff`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/6ed71ffc5b3f0e3275900ea7284e06ddc8d2425c) - **settings/about**: add build information *(commit by @aliernfrog)*
- [`d77d448`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/d77d4482a8c06239838106b097fb458caf586f29) - **l10n**: update translations *(PR #91 by @aliernfrog)*

### üêõ Bug Fixes
- [`59512a6`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/59512a6f043414162c7a3aaca026fe71caa3bddf) - **update-sheet**: version name fading edge color *(commit by @aliernfrog)*
- [`f249bc7`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/f249bc75a4aac257c46febd6c3917e585c4a1cc7) - **maps/materials**: wait for all materials to load *(commit by @aliernfrog)*
- [`d5d1778`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/d5d177842807d91c6f94a66482d4a95f46c05d7a) - **settings/storage**: folder picker on raw path inputs *(commit by @aliernfrog)*
- [`989c8fa`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/989c8fa53ff6d5185753f70c4c606e63a373930d) - **settings/storage**: convert picked uri to path on raw path inputs *(commit by @aliernfrog)*

### :recycle: Refactors
- [`b6a3651`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/b6a3651c3dec36873033156e9d85f8123f1d6d4a) - preference manager *(commit by @aliernfrog)*
